---
title: Spanakopita Inspired Sigara Böreği with Rocket Salad and Chips
description: A recipe that's enjoyed across the Balkans, spanakopita consists of a crumbly white cheese and spinach filling, stuffed between layers of pastry. Here, we're making mini rolls inspired by Turkish sigara böreği for a more handheld experience!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R41_W41_UK_V24161-3_MAIN_low_2-89551750.jpg
